code: /**  * @return Default array capacity  */ public int getDefaultCapacity() {     return defaultCapacity. }
/**  * @param defaultCapacity Default array capacity  */ public void setDefaultCapacity(int defaultCapacity) {     this.defaultCapacity = defaultCapacity. }
/**  * @return Lock fairness  */ public boolean isFair() {     return fair. }
/**  * @param fair Lock fairness  */ public void setFair(boolean fair) {     this.fair = fair. }
@Override public ArrayBlockingQueue<E> create(int capacity) {     return fair == null ? new ArrayBlockingQueue<>(capacity) : new ArrayBlockingQueue<>(capacity, fair). }
